{"tid":623681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大媽晾臭腳　辯稱放低流血不止　空姐焗噴清新劑","createTime":"2018-04-10T08:07:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T08:18:11.000Z","uid":75969,"like":205,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"509e66f87565020a0256951089611212be51c1d9","tid":623681,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T08:07:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180410/photo/bkn-20180410122836312-0410_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180410123142\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180410%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180410122836312-0410_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180410123142&h=91acf294&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180410/photo/bkn-20180410122836312-0410_00822_001_02p.jpg?20180410123142\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180410%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180410122836312-0410_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20180410123142&h=c9b25bbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日有網民於社交群組「巴打絲打 Facebook Club」發貼，指於泰國回香港的航機上，遇到大媽晾腳，期間更聞到陣陣臭味，即使空姐再三勸告亦徒勞無功。有乘客直斥大媽行為自私！<br />\n<br />\n發貼者星期一晚表示，從泰國乘搭航機回港時，有一名大媽施展「軟骨功」，將脫掉鞋的右腳晾於前座上方位置，並露出包紮好的腳趾公。他表示當時有乘客開始反映有臭味傳出，機艙人員亦馬上對國語大媽作出勸導。<br />\n<br />\n不過，該大媽並沒有理會，反而向空姐拿毛氈包腳，更辯稱：「腳趾公受傷，如果放隻腳落嚟會流血不止」。空姐只好不停噴空氣清新劑辟味。<br />\n<br />\n到了吃飯時間，發貼者大嘆「真係頂唔順」，再一次向空姐表示「佢咁嘅行為我真係食唔到飯」。惟經空姐再三要求，大媽亦不願放低腳。<br />\n<br />\n發貼者表示，落機時有一名外籍人士鬧爆大媽：「你真係有需要全飛機去容忍你兩母子嘅自私行為？」不過大媽未有理會，最後更健步如飛般急步離開。<br />\n<br />\n貼文一出，不少網民怒轟大媽行為「自私」：「冇文化真係冇計」、「好樣衰」、「隔住個芒都覺得臭」。另有網民獻計︰「應該利用群情洶湧既（嘅）狀況逼佢放低」、「扮臭到嘔，然後直接嘔落佢個身到（度）」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180410/bkn-20180410122836312-0410_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180410%2Fbkn-20180410122836312-0410_00822_001.html&d=14dy5Za6T0yLZEhG0Vyge%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=12ae68fe\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180410/bkn-20180410122836312-0410_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a14e9f1018bf594e447061f08e6b8ad23cf4b56","tid":623681,"uid":94454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T08:13:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d97a212fb5c51657753be96287097a038d99b5f","tid":623681,"uid":38820,"like":91,"dislike":1,"score":90,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T08:13:54.000Z","msg":"隔住個moon都覺得臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba400314a36302b00fc4bd084d548462fb3e7f7c","tid":623681,"uid":72009,"like":10,"dislike":10,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T08:15:32.000Z","msg":"揾腳膠奶下"},{"pid":"038f37e77a9a1f95351a33869853ad9dd5464256","tid":623681,"uid":67500,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T08:17:30.000Z","msg":"咁斯文做乜，大喝佢呀嘛"},{"pid":"7bca81adf5d94846192c8597959855fe51721416","tid":623681,"uid":31215,"like":4,"dislike":20,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T08:22:57.000Z","msg":"隔離坐個腳膠應該會扯到食唔到飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da211ac01be0e9771b44e6bf322ab8a4a2b4724d","tid":623681,"uid":128600,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T08:25:36.000Z","msg":"飛返轉頭掉佢落機"},{"pid":"5a040a09cc62bbdf1801a3a872e18abb5839e573","tid":623681,"uid":17213,"like":24,"dislike":20,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T08:33:12.000Z","msg":"對付呢種人 只有賤鬥賤<br />\n例如係佢隔離放屁、學佢隆腳、擦白花油、放臭蛋等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c3226cb0d37d1714aece42a7be8e2998d4c710","tid":623681,"uid":79893,"like":224,"dislike":1,"score":223,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T08:33:55.000Z","msg":"飛機係半空嗰時有乘客唔合作<br />\n空姐完全有權綁起佢直到落機<br />\n唔明點解嗰陣啲空姐唔行使呢個權利"},{"pid":"